{"tid":1618802,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[要物資！］禁蒙面法！區區開花！今晚出去一齊開花既手足全部入黎！","createTime":"2019-10-04T06:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T07:05:44.000Z","uid":198233,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"46c97e7256faf0f434b71aaa0113be022011161c","tid":1618802,"uid":198233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:34:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">相信未來幾日<br />\n甚至一週 幾週<br />\n到到都有仗要打<br />\n你地出得黎 就預左要有心理準備去做野<br />\n唔係叫你一定要搞黨鐵做勇武<br />\n但最少希望你地可以補返d物資<br />\n我發現<span style=\"color: red;\">物資</span>愈黎愈唔足夠<br />\n10月1都可以見到<br />\n基本物資唔講啦<br />\n大家都買<span style=\"color: red;\">鐵線鐵鏈</span> <br />\n見到鎖撚住個黨鐵鐵閘位！<br />\n或者一人一枝<span style=\"color: red;\">啤酒樽</span> 都夠哂做啦<br />\n唔洗你地扔 幫手帶出黎都好啊！！！<br />\n需要大家去分工！<br />\n有咩野都主動幫手<br />\n例如後排可以整<span style=\"color: red;\">拆鐵拆磚</span>整土魔法<br />\n主動d 求下大家 我地無退路！！<br />\n背水一戰 就算呢場係硬仗 唔可以輸<br />\n<br />\n我已經隨時被捕既心理準備（我會好撚小心）<br />\n求大家再行多步<br />\n主動多一步好嗎<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"1a24bf71d2974997f6cb5ec1fbad9d0225473213","tid":1618802,"uid":198233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:35:36.000Z","msg":"好啦 自推10"},{"pid":"9fcf316c9d951137c01282b04b562c33dd4e40b4","tid":1618802,"uid":198233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:35:58.000Z","msg":"9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1572c0463b85791592d426c867b07dd8737cb0b4","tid":1618802,"uid":198233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:36:48.000Z","msg":"8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66541ee75469deee4a0203d9f416619b960a302e","tid":1618802,"uid":198233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:37:15.000Z","msg":"7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee440b1d2f74ac8f71f291c0ec81daefe8fbc8e7","tid":1618802,"uid":198233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"